title: Was Trump Rushed Off Stage After Someone Yelled ‘Chrissy Teigen’s Here’?
subtitle: The U.S. president and the model lobbed a few insults at each other on social media in September 2019.
author: Dan Evon
vclaim: A video shows U.S. President Donald Trump being rushed off stage after someone yelled that model Chrissy Teigen was in the audience.
